caption-lab
===========

This project is a standalone experiment harness that reproduces the
caption-correction / forced-alignment pipeline of PalmierPro. It is a
DERIVATIVE WORK of PalmierPro and is therefore licensed under the
GNU General Public License v3.0 (see LICENSE).

Upstream / origin
-----------------
PalmierPro — https://github.com/palmier-io/palmier-pro (GPL-3.0)
The code here was extracted from a private BYOK fork of that project.

Provenance of the extracted sources
-----------------------------------
Files whose logic originates from upstream palmier-io/palmier-pro
(present in upstream at extraction time):
  - Sources/CaptionLab/Transcription.swift      (Apple SpeechTranscriber front-end)
  - Sources/CaptionLab/CaptionBuilder.swift      (only the `units` / CJK helpers)
  - Sources/CaptionLab/Models.swift              (ContentSegment, from MediaManifest.swift)
  - Sources/CaptionLab/WordCutPlanner.swift      (+ RippleEngine.mergeRanges)

Files added in the fork (not present upstream), extracted here:
  - Sources/CaptionLab/TranscriptCorrector.swift (Gemini text correction + 1:1 writeback)
  - Sources/CaptionLab/GeminiClient.swift        (BYOK Gemini client; key via GEMINI_API_KEY)
  - Sources/CaptionLab/MediaDescriber.swift      (deep content-map generation path)
  - Sources/CaptionLab/CaptionPipeline.swift     (glossary harvest + retranscribe, de-tangled from EditorViewModel)
  - Sources/CaptionLab/CutStutters.swift         (disfluency/stutter cut; defaultFillers from EditorViewModel+AutoCut)
  - the ForcedAligner text-alignment logic

Additions original to caption-lab (not from PalmierPro):
  - The SwiftUI GUI (AppEntry, ContentView, TrackViews, TimelineView, ControlsPanel,
    ResultsPanels, PipelineViewModel, Theme) — the multi-clip track, waveform timeline,
    joined AVMutableComposition playback, and A/B chip lanes.
  - The Qwen MLX forced-aligner backend: Sources/CaptionLab/QwenAligner.swift and
    aligner/qwen_align.py, wrapping mlx-community/Qwen3-ForcedAligner-0.6B-8bit via mlx-audio.
  - setup.sh, CLAUDE.md, README.md.

Modifications from the originals
--------------------------------
Key loading was changed from Keychain to the GEMINI_API_KEY environment variable;
EditorViewModel-bound methods were lifted into free functions with view-model plumbing
removed; algorithms were kept byte-faithful. See git history for details.
